{"tid":1159630,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 英國入境取消Landing Card","createTime":"2019-05-17T23:53:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-18T00:33:27.000Z","uid":126675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"51e29b7d21306d023ea79a6456e70cef9d5a4df5","tid":1159630,"uid":126675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T23:53:02.000Z","msg":"<strong>All landing cards for international passengers arriving in the UK will be scrapped from Monday.</strong><br />\n<br />\nLanding cards are currently filled in by passengers arriving by air or sea from outside the European Economic Area.<br />\n<br />\nBorder Force director general Paul Lincoln, in a letter to staff, said it would &quot;help meet the challenge of growing passenger numbers&quot;.<br />\n<br />\nBut unions warned it risked weakening immigration controls.<br />\n<br />\nAround 16 million landing cards are issued every year and they are used to record what is said to border staff on arrival, as well as the reasons for travel and conditions of entry.<br />\n<br />\nThe Home Office had agreed to scrap them for seven countries, including the US and Australia, from June, but has now decided to go further.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-48297695?ocid=socialflow_facebook&amp;ns_campaign=bbcnews&amp;ns_mchannel=social&amp;ns_source=facebook&amp;fbclid=IwAR0_HXlPXiMrndNY_PviMgyHjqZnOe3o-pB9e5uFC8W5Vi_n9G_9ubuE1Yo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-48297695%3Focid%3Dsocialflow_facebook%26ns_campaign%3Dbbcnews%26ns_mchannel%3Dsocial%26ns_source%3Dfacebook%26fbclid%3DIwAR0_HXlPXiMrndNY_PviMgyHjqZnOe3o-pB9e5uFC8W5Vi_n9G_9ubuE1Yo&d=LRk9npnliL4HefRMP%2BWOkFT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=3b3d6cdf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-48297695%3Focid%3Dsocialflow_facebook%26ns_campaign%3Dbbcnews%26ns_mchannel%3Dsocial%26ns_source%3Dfacebook%26fbclid%3DIwAR0_HXlPXiMrndNY_PviMgyHjqZnOe3o-pB9e5uF